Residents of Kiserian, Ongata Rongai and Karen will today protest against rogue matatu drivers plying the route.The protests follow the accident on Sunday in which a matatu overturned on Lang ata Road killing four people and injuring six.Residents said they will walk from Tusky s in Rongai to the Lang ata cemetery. We are saying enough is enough. The reckless matatu culture and police complicity in the madness will not be accepted as lives are being lost, a resident said.